		<div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
	
								<h3 class="widget-heading"><span>CSO Responsibilities</span></h3>
				
						<ul>
<li type="disc">Answering the public's questions.</li>
<li type="disc">Patrolling campus grounds.</li>
<li type="disc">Assisting with community functions and athletic events.</li>
<li type="disc">Providing general security services for special events on campus.</li>
<li type="disc">Conducting nightly safety escorts.</li>
<li type="disc">Opening and closing campus facilities.</li>
</ul>
				
			</div>
	</div>
	
									
								
						
							    
			
						
		
	<div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-6">
