																				<section aria-labelledby="section-3-heading" id="section-3">
						<div class="container">
												<div class="row">
								<div class="col-xs-12">
									<h2 class="section-heading text-left" id="section-3-heading"><span>Safety Escorts</span></h2>
								</div>
							</div>
										
    									<div class="row">
		
    							
								
						
							    
			
						
		
	<div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-8">
		<div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
	
								
				
						<h1><img alt="safety escort helping cyclist" class="responsive" height="100%" src="img/safetyescort-banner.jpg" width="auto"/></h1>
<div class="content">
<div class="text">
<p>The CSO Safety Escort program is a free service provided to members of the UCI community as a safe alternative to walking alone at night.</p>
<p>CSO's are equipped with radios that allow them to keep in constant communication with the Police Department.</p>
<p>When requesting an escort, please provide the dispatcher with the following information:</p>
<ul>
<ul><ol>
<li>Your name</li>
<li>Your location</li>
<li>Your cell phone number</li>
<li>Your destination</li>
</ol></ul>
</ul>
<p>A uniformed CSO will then meet you and escort you to your destination.</p>
<p>This program is not intended to replace existing transportation services such as the <a href="http://www.shuttle.uci.edu/" target="_blank">Campus Shuttles</a> or to discourage individuals from walking in groups. Rather it is designed to enhance campus community safety.</p>
<p><a id="escorts"></a>&#65279;</p>
<p>&#65279;</p>
</div>
</div>
				
			</div>
	</div>
	
									
								
						
							    
			
						
		
	<div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-4">
		<div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
	
								
				
						<div style="border-left: medium #eeeeee solid;">
<h3 class="bucket-header" style="background-color: #0064a4; line-height: 30px; color: white;">&#160;&#160;<strong>Don't walk alone&#160;at night</strong></h3>
<p style="margin: 0 0 0 8px;">The service is available 24 hours a day,7 days<br/>a week.</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 0 8px;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 0 8px;">For a free Safety Escort,<br/>call <strong><a href="tel:949.824.7233" title="Safety Escort Service 949.824.7233">(949) 824-SAFE</a> (7233)</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 0 8px;">&#160;</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 0 8px;"><a href="safety_escort_faq.php" title="Safet Escort Frequently ASked Questions"><strong>Frequently Asked Questions</strong></a></p>
</div>
				
			</div>
